# For Vercel / production, set:
# DATABASE_URL (Vercel Postgres or Turso)
# RESEND_API_KEY
# RESEND_FROM (e.g. noreply@yourdomain.com)
# DIGEST_EMAIL (recipient for daily digest)
# CRON_SECRET (for securing cron endpoint)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL (e.g. https://your-app.vercel.app)
